content: standujar: This week, standujar focused on significant bug fixes and optimizations within the core `elizaos/eliza` repository, merging several large and complex PRs to resolve TypeScript build errors (#6218), correct encryption logic (#6217), and optimize data migrations (#6215). In parallel, they initiated a major feature push by opening four PRs to add streaming support across the core application and multiple plugins. This work reflects a primary focus on bug fixes (45%) and new feature development (23%).
